bel Prize<\/a> in 1993. On May 29, 2012, she received the <a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Presidential_Medal_of_Freedom\" title=\"Presidential Medal of Freedom\">Presidential Medal of Freedom<\/a>.<\/p>","name":"Toni Morrison","place_of_birth":"Lorain, Ohio","place_of_death":null,"text":"Toni Morrison , Literature, 1993","year":1993.0}